{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 236 "B
y the above (Sturm sequence arguments) each of the eight terms has no \+
zeros.  Therefore, each of the eight terms has constant sign.\n\nSince
 the value at x = 0 of each of the eight terms is positive, each of th
e eight terms is positive.\n" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 54 "Hence,  t
he partial derivative of HH1 with respect to " }{TEXT 290 1 "a" }
{TEXT -1 14 "  is positive " }{TEXT 291 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 68 "Hence,  the partial derivative of HH1 with respect to r  is neg
ative" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 49 "Hence, HH1 is increasing \+
in a and decreasing in r" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "
" 0 "" {TEXT -1 40 "Hence, HH1 maximizes at a = l2 and r = 0" }}{PARA 
0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 28 "Note:  we alrea
dy showed in " }{TEXT 322 62 "campbell-maple-substep2a.mws --  verify \+
